---
title: System Sequence Diagram - Start New Game & Set Policy
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor Player as Actor
    participant System as :System

    Player->>System: startNewGame()
    System-->>Player: requestCityDetails()
    
    Note right of Player: Player inputs name and selects Strategy (e.g., GreenPolicy)
    Player->>System: configureGame("Topolinia", "GreenPolicy")
    
    System-->>Player: displayCityDashboard(initialState)